<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your registration is waiting</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: #F8F4EF; color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #D4A017; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .brand { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #1A3C5E; }
    .tagline { font-size: 11px; color: #5a6e7a; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
    h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: #1A3C5E; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
    p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .cta-link { display: inline-block; background: #D4A017; color: #0d1b2a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 3px; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e0d8cc; font-size: 11px; color: #5a6e7a; }
    a { color: #3d7a8a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">Dnyanpith</div>
      <div class="tagline">Environment changes outcomes.</div>
    </div>

    <h1>Your spot is still open.</h1>

    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>You started a registration for <strong>{{programDisplayName}}</strong>{{#if batchName}} — {{batchName}}{{/if}} but the payment didn't go through.</p>
    <p>Seats are limited. If you'd like to hold yours, complete the payment now.</p>

    <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
      <a href="{{retryUrl}}" class="cta-link">Complete Registration</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you ran into an issue or want to talk it through, just reply to this email. Arjun reads every one.</p>

    <p>— Arjun, Dnyanpith</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Dnyanpith Abhyasika Pvt. Ltd. · Ambajogai, Maharashtra<br />
      <a href="mailto:hello@dnyanpith.org">hello@dnyanpith.org</a><br />
      <small>You're receiving this because you started a registration. If that wasn't you, ignore this email.</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
